<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>1-325.324</num>
  <heading>Reporting requirements.</heading>
  <text>Beginning December 1, 2017, the grant-managing entity shall submit a semiannual report to the Council of all District funds allocated, which includes:</text>
  <para>
    <num>(1)</num>
    <text>Detailed grantee data;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(2)</num>
    <text>Performance measures and performance outcomes under each grant;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(3)</num>
    <text>The specific services provided under each grant;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(4)</num>
    <text>The entity providing the services, if one other than the grantee;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(5)</num>
    <text>The time period of delivery of the services;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(6)</num>
    <text>The type of service provided;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(7)</num>
    <text>The actual amount paid for the services; and</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(8)</num>
    <text>The amount of other expenditures under the grant, if any.</text>
  </para>
